  "title": "Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure designs meet printing specifications and color profiles.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with project team and print production teams to ensure designs are optimized for efficient and high-quality printing.   </li>\n  <li>Utilize color management techniques to ensure accurate and consistent colors in print output.   </li>\n  <li>Understand different printing / production methods, material types,   finishes, and techniques to create designs suitable for each project.   </li>\n  <li>Manage multiple projects simultaneously, meeting deadlines for design and print production.   </li>\n  <li>Ensure all datas are stored in company server accordingly.   </li>\n  <li>Fluency in current graphic design practices; such as Adobe Photoshop; Adobe Illustrator and Adobe InDesign.</li>\n</ul>",
